==比撒列的祖父户珥==
属于[[犹大支派|犹大支派]]，是Uri的父亲，比撒列的祖父<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.biblegateway.com/passage/?search=Exodus%2031:2;35:30;38:22;%201%20Chronicles%202:19-20;%202%20Chronicles%201:5;&version=9; |title=Ex. 31:2; 35:30; 38:22; 1 Chron. 2:19-20; 2 Chron. 1:5 |accessdate=2007-05-15 |archive-date=2007-03-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070311003442/http://www.biblegateway.com/passage/?search=Exodus%2031:2;35:30;38:22;%201%20Chronicles%202:19-20;%202%20Chronicles%201:5;&version=9; |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他也许与摩西的助手户珥是同一个人，但不能确定。

==米甸国王户珥==
在摩西时，[[以利亚撒|以利亚撒]]的儿子[[非尼哈|非尼哈]]率领1万2千人的以色列军队远征，米甸国王户珥和米甸的另外四王一同被杀，比珥的儿子占卜者[[巴蘭|巴蘭]]也同时被杀<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.biblegateway.com/passage/?search=Numbers%2031:8;%20Joshua%2013:21;&version=9; |title=民数记31:8；约书亚记13:21 |accessdate=2007-05-15 |archive-date=2007-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070302021752/http://www.biblegateway.com/passage/?search=Numbers%2031:8;%20Joshua%2013:21;&version=9; |dead-url=no }}</ref>。


